1
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:15,240
This is a good story.

2
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:16,039
And then?

3
00:01:17,080 --> 00:01:18,320
Give me a second.

4
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,640
Are you full?

5
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:24,280
Yes.

6
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:25,960
On the road,

7
00:01:26,039 --> 00:01:28,170
it's hard to get meat even on holidays.

8
00:01:29,240 --> 00:01:30,840
What happened to the rabbit?

9
00:01:31,160 --> 00:01:31,960
The rabbit?

10
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,560
Did you guys roast it?

11
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:39,520
We are always rushing on the road.

12
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:41,840
We don't have time to catch rabbits.

13
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:43,280
Let's go for a walk.

14
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,560
Let's go.

15
00:01:48,600 --> 00:01:49,520
Boss,

16
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:52,000
your local dishes are the most authentic we've ever had.

17
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,800
Wish you a booming business!

18
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:54,000
Come again next time.

19
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:55,720
Let's go.

20
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,960
I'm so full.

21
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,800
Can you two lend me some money?

22
00:02:10,840 --> 00:02:11,640
What's wrong?

23
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:14,690
It seems we didn't pay for the meal we just had.

24
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:16,520
Right.

25
00:02:16,520 --> 00:02:17,800
What should we do?

26
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,720
How about

27
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,200
we leave you there as collateral,

28
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,320
and you can wash dishes to pay for it?

29
00:02:24,800 --> 00:02:25,720
Whatever it takes.

30
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,720
A real man is always upright.

31
00:02:27,720 --> 00:02:29,380
You have to pay for your meals.

32
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,850
With your appetite,

33
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,380
the boss would lose money.

34
00:02:33,320 --> 00:02:35,240
All right, stop teasing him.

35
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:37,920
Don't worry.

36
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,720
I've already paid with my phone.

37
00:02:40,920 --> 00:02:42,000
Pay with this?

38
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:43,400
Yeah.

39
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,320
Everyone uses mobile payment now.

40
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:48,040
Who still uses cash?

41
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,730
Someone is singing.

42
00:03:14,440 --> 00:03:16,320
Is this

43
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,450
street performing?

44
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:19,960
He is live-streaming.

45
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:23,079
It's a way to show talents to the public.

46
00:03:23,079 --> 00:03:25,340
It's also a lifestyle for modern people.

47
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:27,200
Use this

48
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:29,800
to let more people know him through the Internet.

49
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:30,800
Live-streaming?

50
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,180
Can you do it anywhere?

51
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,520
That's right.

52
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,640
Any corner of the world.

53
00:03:38,240 --> 00:03:40,170
How long does it take to reach them?

54
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,320
In seconds.

55
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:43,120
Instantly.

56
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,760
Just like

57
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:47,240
you and me talking face to face.

58
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,000
Talking face to face?

59
00:04:05,840 --> 00:04:07,440
Why are you in the little box?

60
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:09,320
What little box?

61
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:11,360
This is a face-to-face video call.

62
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:16,920
All right.

63
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:18,200
I know you like to play tricks.

64
00:04:18,200 --> 00:04:19,000
Come back.

65
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,520
Come look.

66
00:04:25,520 --> 00:04:27,560
How are my photography skills?

67
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,800
Professional, right?

68
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:31,000
Your little box can also take pictures?

69
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,000
What little box?

70
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:35,890
I told you modern people rely on it to survive.

71
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,040
I wonder

72
00:04:39,040 --> 00:04:40,400
where the letter I sent to Grandpa

73
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:41,320
is now.

74
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,000
But

75
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,640
your modern technology is really convenient.

76
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,400
Hurry up.

77
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:18,320
If we don't leave, I'm afraid Yiyi will ask for his WeChat.

78
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,840
You guys ran away.

79
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:24,440
Why did you two run?

80
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,960
Weren't we creating an opportunity for you?

81
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:29,400
What opportunity?

82
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:32,400
I was just mesmerized by his singing, okay?

83
00:05:34,520 --> 00:05:35,600
As for you,

84
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,320
Yaoyao.

85
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:38,920
It's getting late.

86
00:05:39,440 --> 00:05:41,640
Where is this old fossil going to sleep?

87
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,360
The sky is my blanket, the earth is my bed.

88
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,560
I can sleep anywhere.

89
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:49,920
Where could an old fossil like him sleep?

90
00:05:49,920 --> 00:05:52,000
Don't we have a sofa in the living room?

91
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,240
Let him make do with it.

92
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,240
What do you think?

93
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,480
The living room costs money too.

94
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,610
Who is paying for it?

95
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,440
I'll cover his share.

96
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,380
You'll have to make do.

97
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:03,520
Make do?

98
00:06:04,960 --> 00:06:06,440
Compared to the environment in Yunnan-Burma,

99
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:09,170
your living room is already very luxurious to me.

100
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,400
But rest assured,

101
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,130
I will definitely pay you back.

102
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,720
Your pockets are cleaner than your face.

103
00:06:14,720 --> 00:06:16,360
How will you pay us back?

104
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,400
I can drive.

105
00:06:18,920 --> 00:06:19,760
Drive?

106
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:23,640
With your ID, that's driving without a license nowadays.

107
00:06:23,760 --> 00:06:24,640
Besides,

108
00:06:24,640 --> 00:06:26,960
do you know how to drive our modern cars?

109
00:06:28,520 --> 00:06:31,320
Then give us an idea, Strategist Zhang.

110
00:06:39,320 --> 00:06:41,240
It's not that I don't have an idea.

111
00:06:41,520 --> 00:06:44,120
But it requires a little sacrifice from you.

112
00:06:45,520 --> 00:06:46,360
Sacrifice?

113
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,000
You two,

114
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:54,260
what's with that look?

115
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:56,680
I'm a law-abiding good citizen.

116
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:59,650
I wouldn't do the illegal things you're thinking of.

117
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,320
So how should I cooperate with you?

118
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,720
Use this.

119
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:14,840
Let me use this to record your story.

120
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:15,720
No refusing,

121
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,380
and no going back on your word.

122
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,360
My story?

123
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:23,760
You were already filming him while eating.

124
00:07:24,080 --> 00:07:25,880
That was an advance audition.

125
00:07:26,760 --> 00:07:27,760
Let me tell you,

126
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:30,680
meeting beautiful and kind-hearted people like me and Yaoyao,

127
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,340
you should be secretly happy.

128
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:36,560
Calling you a strategist is understating it.

129
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,800
We really should call you Director Zhang.

130
00:07:38,800 --> 00:07:39,520
Let's go.

131
00:07:39,520 --> 00:07:40,360
Let's go home.

132
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:41,880
Come with us.

133
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,240
Right, face.

134
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:53,640
Right, face.

135
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,440
Left, face.

136
00:07:57,320 --> 00:07:58,440
Left, face.

137
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,440
About, face.

138
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,440
Left, face.

139
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,520
Right, face.

140
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:11,040
Right, face.

141
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:15,720
About, face.

142
00:08:17,280 --> 00:08:19,560
Right, face.

143
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:30,960
About, face.

144
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:45,480
Left, face.

145
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,320
Left, face.

146
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,600
Right, face.

147
00:08:52,280 --> 00:08:53,120
Lin Yaozu.

148
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,460
You're up so early.

149
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,400
Where is Director Zhang?

150
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,330
Director Zhang?

151
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:00,040
Oh,

152
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:03,200
she's revising the script in her dreams right now.

153
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:06,000
Is this military training?

154
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,610
This is military drill.

155
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:09,690
Military drill?

156
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,960
Haven't we already won?

157
00:09:13,960 --> 00:09:15,280
Why do we still need military drill?

158
00:09:15,280 --> 00:09:16,160
Left, face.

159
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,960
Left, face.

160
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,600
Every school year,

161
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:24,760
schools organize military training.

162
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:27,200
It's to commemorate the predecessors

163
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:29,080
who sacrificed their lives for the victory of New China.

164
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:31,740
It reminds us to better cherish our present life

165
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:34,680
and is also a kind of training for young people.

166
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:37,980
Is it something every student must experience?

167
00:09:38,680 --> 00:09:39,800
You could say that.

168
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:43,720
Every generation of ours

169
00:09:45,640 --> 00:09:47,000
has its own experiences,

170
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,680
and its own mission.

171
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:51,820
It's a good tradition to keep.

172
00:09:52,280 --> 00:09:54,010
Even though they are students,

173
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:56,480
they would still go to the battlefield.

174
00:09:57,600 --> 00:09:59,240
I believe if needed,

175
00:09:59,640 --> 00:10:01,640
every Chinese would step forward,

176
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:03,610
even sacrificing their lives.

177
00:10:07,080 --> 00:10:09,840
I sincerely swear.
